        "subject": "LU-11111 mdd: don't assert on ORPHAN flag",
        "message": "LU-11111 mdd: don't assert on ORPHAN flag\n\nLFSCK may add an orphan back to its original parent, and it will make\nthis object into a normal one, but with ORHPHAN flag set, in case\nthis object is unlinked again later, don't assert on ORPHAN flag\nin mdd_orphan_insert(), but print a warning instead.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I0bd00b862900c1ec5f73ce13787489c81c41463b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
